 major part of the colour excess\nappears to be either intrinsic or reddening that arises in the immediate\nenvironment of supernova, rather than interstellar reddening in host galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2009 06:53:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
