 governing the ratio between the generalized degree and the traditional\ndegree. The analysis also shows that nodes with more uniform weights tend to\ncluster with nodes that also have more uniform weights among themselves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2009 11:23:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2009 08:42:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 28 Nov 2010 08:51:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-22"}
